description: Try our easy to follow Creamy Zucchini With Walnuts recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Creamy Zucchini With Walnuts Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Heat the oil in a large frying pan, add the onion and cook for 5 minutes until soft. Add the zucchini and celery and cook for 4-5 minutes until soft and starting to brown.
Add the cheese and cook for 2-3 minutes until melted. Stir in the walnuts, season to taste with salt and pepper and serve immediately.
